products.title: Premium One 35 in. W x 71.7 in. x 18.5 in. D 4-Shelf Resin Freestanding Cabinet in Grey
products.description: Durable storage solution helps organize your space. Heavy-duty construction handles significant weight. Easy assembly with included hardware.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is this waterproof?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: This container is water-resistant but not fully waterproof. It will protect contents from splashes and light rain but should not be submerged.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can these be stacked?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, these are designed to stack securely. Check the specifications for the maximum recommended stacking height.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is the weight capacity?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Please refer to the specifications for exact weight limits. Distribute heavy items evenly and don't exceed the recommended capacity.
